data.description: Must see this well cared for home being sold by the original owners. The home is smoke free and pet free. The main floor is spacious and comfortable with a formal dining, living room, great room and spacious kitchen. Outside the kitchen is the patio and oversized backyard including a putting green!The upper level provides a ton of natural light with a large primary bedroom that includes a 5-piece en-suite bathroom and a large primary closet. The second floor also features 3 additional bedrooms with ample closet space. Downstairs is a full basement waiting for the new owner's creativity to make their own. The neighborhood's parks create a friendly and lively atmosphere for all residents. very close to shopping, dining, and a quick commute to DIA. Hurry, it will not last!
